"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"> “We have to stand against this practice. \\\\[...\\\\] This is just another way to nickel and dime players with cosmetics rather than focusing on making quality products with depth. We have to let companies know this is anti-consumer.”\\n\\n“I'm not entirely against the concept of using an NFT style system for digital games. For example, actually owning your digital copy rather than just a license so you can sell it to another user's account. That's actually the future of digital gaming. What I'm against is how Ubisoft are doing it with in-game items,” they added.\",\"timestamp\":1639139401,\"title\":\"that were due to mature by the end of 2020,\"},\"digest\":\"6epzSZABymYdU1SRD10qq18NhlqkS1Y2v5jxXZ5h18E\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x0D4803a4c35E26B8704e764dD1E0262ea2943919\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"0SoSaZ5C4555EdvOGu4Mg9qu8Y8QMz3Eacann3hKFFY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eSWCeLJc7efzyT-3-0Uy-opFRsaVEM1R9CgN9x1_h6w\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"6h9HXGJCHMbo0Oabo30BzLnzkt4yEWACxIFYHgXO7idFhYkBNuKqnhsqCK2CkCcJWNS8i7O3djHoKsemDqm_UA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x8177f3da3e45687b881e79697bc8de24d6fb0dada951e8b6d854c7249b632f266ba8b60398d17143b38fd8bf3861e3c073a355ede658875c33f9a262c5a967c71b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"0SoSaZ5C4555EdvOGu4Mg9qu8Y8QMz3Eacann3hKFFY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eSWCeLJc7efzyT-3-0Uy-opFRsaVEM1R9CgN9x1_h6w\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"6epzSZABymYdU1SRD10qq18NhlqkS1Y2v5jxXZ5h18E\"}"